room_title: Escape room "The Photographer’s Darkroom and Studio" by The Hallway Escape in Port Huron
room_address: 218 Huron Ave Suite B Port Huron, MI 48060
room_description: You’ve had so many ads popping up on your social media and google searches for this amazing photographer in town, so many that it almost seems like you’ve been targeted. But of course, that’s just your mind playing games on you, right? You entered a contest for a free photo session and actually won! So, here you are, for your photoshoot.
